# Cross-Agent Delegation Demo — Claude delegating to OpenCode
# Usage: just demo delegation-demo

Output assets/delegation-demo.gif

Require cru

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "GruvboxDark"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "/tmp/cru-demo-wrapper"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show
Sleep 30s
